@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Bearing Categories";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <h1 class="mt-4">Bearing Categories</h1>
    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a asp-controller="Bearings" asp-action="Index">Bearings</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Categories</li>
        </ol>
    </nav>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Ball Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Ball bearings are the most common type of bearing and can handle both radial and thrust loads.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Single row ball bearings</li>
                        <li>Double row ball bearings</li>
                        <li>Angular contact ball bearings</li>
                        <li>Self-aligning ball bearings</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Ball Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    42 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Roller Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Roller bearings use cylinders instead of balls, providing more surface area for load distribution.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cylindrical roller bearings</li>
                        <li>Tapered roller bearings</li>
                        <li>Spherical roller bearings</li>
                        <li>Needle roller bearings</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-success">View Roller Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    28 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Thrust Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Thrust bearings are designed specifically to handle thrust loads in one direction.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Ball thrust bearings</li>
                        <li>Roller thrust bearings</li>
                        <li>Tapered thrust bearings</li>
                        <li>Washers and thrust plates</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-info">View Thrust Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    15 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Mounted Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Mounted bearings come pre-assembled with a housing, making installation easier.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Pillow block bearings</li>
                        <li>Flange bearings</li>
                        <li>Take-up bearings</li>
                        <li>Cartridge bearings</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-warning">View Mounted Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    23 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Linear Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Linear bearings enable smooth motion along a single axis, ideal for sliding applications.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Linear ball bearings</li>
                        <li>Linear roller bearings</li>
                        <li>Linear guides</li>
                        <li>Linear slides</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-danger">View Linear Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    17 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-header bg-secondary text-white">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Specialty Bearings</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Specialty bearings designed for unique applications and requirements.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Miniature bearings</li>
                        <li>Ceramic bearings</li>
                        <li>Water-resistant bearings</li>
                        <li>High-temperature bearings</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="d-grid">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">View Specialty Bearings</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer text-muted">
                    11 products in this category
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 